   "Situation: I was given a solo for the church play.  At practice when it came time for me to sing, my voice cracked and I lost the solo.\nDistorted Thought: I can't sing.\nRational Response: I have been singing a lot and was not taking enough time to rest and prepare, and as a result, I faced some consequences. In the future, I will try to take better care of my voice so I can do the things I love!",
   "Situation: I was given a solo for the church play.  At practice when it came time for me to sing, my voice cracked and I lost the solo.\nDistorted Thought: I can't sing.\nRational Response: I made a mistake at a crucial moment and faced some consequences. I know I'm a good singer, otherwise I wouldn't have gotten the solo at all. I will keep practicing and see if I can get some feedback from the director about how to improve for the next play.",
