   'Situation: A potential client decided to work with another company.\nDistorted Thought: I failed our company & myself.\nRational Response: I am not a failure because a client made a different decision than I wanted them to. I am doing the best work I can, which is why I feel so invested in this outcome. If one client decision is enough to make me feel like a complete failure, I will take that as a sign that I need to be more kind to myself.',
