   "Situation: I was at work and sent info for an ad to our local newspaper. They called me later and said my boss had over-ridden everything and sent them new info.\nDistorted Thought: He shouldn't assign me a task if he doesn't trust my work.\nRational Response: My boss wanted to provide different information, I did not know that beforehand. This is not a reflection of my work.",
