   'Situation: When doing some piecework online, I was told that my work was not good.\nDistorted Thought: I worked hard on these jobs, and was sure I had done well.\nRational Response: My style of work may not fit the company that hired me. I want to be open and ask for specific feedback on their expectations.',
   'Situation: While I was at work, my supervisor questioned my decision in a negative tone infront of my peers.\nDistorted Thought: She needs to stop discussing this.\nRational Response: My supervisor was being unfair to me by discussing this in front of people and I was hurt. I should talk to her in private about this and how I would like to receive feedback in the future.',
   "Situation: My boss yelled at me\nDistorted Thought: I'm feeling sad\nRational Response: Not a great situation to get yelled at, but everyone does it sometimes",
