   'Situation: Rejected from my dream company\nDistorted Thought: I never get what I want\nRational Response: Never? Think about the instances when I was able to achieve what I wanted',
   "Situation: I found a job I thought was perfect for me in the field I used to work in and love very much. A few days after putting in a resume and lining up several references, I found out the job was filled and I didn't even get so much as an acknowledgment of my application much less an interview when I was extremely qualified.\nDistorted Thought: why can't I ever get anything I want\nRational Response: There are many reasons why the position could have been filled including it was filled prior to my submission.",
