   'Situation: I tried to make friends with people but they kept ignoring me.\nDistorted Thought: I am not interesting\nRational Response: It takes time to meet new people and to integrate into a new social group where everyone knows each other. I just need to keep trying my best and finding more outlets to interact with people with similar interests to me.',
