   "Situation: I came home to find my spouse had taken all of his things and left a note saying our marriage was over.\nDistorted Thought: My marriage is over.\nRational Response: I am feeling a lot of grief and panic about what this means. If it's the right thing to do, I will work hard to fix this relationship.",
