   'Situation: I saw my best friend kissing with my long time crush\nDistorted Thought: No one cares about me\nRational Response: Seeing my best friend kiss my crush was very hard for me to forget.  There will be other crushes in my life and other people who care about me.  I know my family and other friends care about me.',
   "Situation: My wife, asked me very kindly, to finally clean the bathroom shower in our bathroom, and I got upset by this.\nDistorted Thought: I'm busy doing something else, it's not like I haven't tried to get to that chore!\nRational Response: She is not necessarily telling me that I am not working hard enough on other tasks and demands in our lives. She is communicating her need for support with one specific task. I will work on fulfilling my commitments when I commit to doing so.",
   "Situation: My husband wants a divorce, I've self isolated for years, my brother died\nDistorted Thought: Worthlessness, abandonment, grief\nRational Response: There is no connection between my brother dying and my husband wanting a divorce.",
